{"word":"ἀλαλητός","slug":"ἀλαλητός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀλαλητός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀλαλή'><el>ἀλαλή</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>the shout of victory</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>: <i>war-cry</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>rarely, <i>a cry of woe</i> or <i>wailing</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a loud noise</i>, <el>αὐλῶν</el> <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}